s is a tiny, laid back backpack village, great to spend the night go on a tour through Paracas National Reserve and do a Pisco Wine tasting tour. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read more:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/paracas-peru\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Ballestas Islands of Paracas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130958\/peru-travel-guide-paracas-lima.jpg\" alt=\"peru travel guide paracas lima\"><\/noscript><img width=\"291\" height=\"338\" alt=\"peru travel guide paracas lima\" class=\"wp-image-17155 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1653px) 100vw, 1653px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130958\/peru-travel-guide-paracas-lima.jpg 1653w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130958\/peru-travel-guide-paracas-lima-300x348.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130958\/peru-travel-guide-paracas-lima-600x697.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130958\/peru-travel-guide-paracas-lima-291x338.jpg 291w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130958\/peru-travel-guide-paracas-lima-517x600.jpg 517w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10