  <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h3>Day 5 &#x2013; 6: Huacachina<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The highest sand dunes in South America surrounding a small lagoon with lush-green palm trees. This oasis named Huacachina has to be on your Peru travel itinerary as it is a unique phenomenon. So watch the sunset from the dune top, do a sand buggy tour through the desert and spend the night.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read more:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/huacachina-peru\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Huacachina, the desert oasis of Peru (opens in a new tab)\">Huacachina, the desert oasis of Peru<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130947\/peru-travel-guide-huacachina-desert-oasis.jpg\" alt=\"peru travel guide huacachina desert oasis\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"304\" alt=\"peru travel guide huacachina desert oasis\" class=\"wp-image-17158 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130947\/peru-travel-guide-huacachina-desert-oasis.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130947\/peru-travel-guide-huacachina-desert-oasis-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130947\/peru-travel-guide-huacachina-desert-oasis-600x405.