ontainer\">\n<p><strong>Paracas to Huacachina&#xA0;<\/strong><br>Huachachina is a short 45-minute bus ride from Paracas. Unfortunately, there is no public transport but you can take a taxi from Ica or a bus tour company.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"huacachina peru travel guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"huacachina peru travel guide\" class=\"wp-image-17156 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130955\/huacachina-peru-travel-guide-8