000 years ago. The viewing tower on the side of the highway gives a good look at the drawings such as a tree and hands. Alternatively, book a flight to see all the Nazca lines from above.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/nazca-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Book a tour here (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Book a tour here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines.jpg\" alt=\"peru travel guide nazca lines\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"peru travel guide nazca lines\" class=\"wp-image-17203 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair