eo-block__wrapper--breakout\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/VideoObject\">\n                <h3 class=\"video-block__wrapper-title\" itemprop=\"name\">Peru<\/h3>\n\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnail\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133228\/Thumb-peru-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Peru\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133228\/Thumb-peru-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2019-07-29 17:26:26\">\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block video-block--mediavine\">\n                    <div class=\"video-block__embed\">\n                        <div class=\"mv-video-target mv-video-id-wyzigqtjwnjgcrswii4q\" data-video-id=\"wyzigqtjwnjgcrswii4q\" data-volume=\"70\" data-ratio=\"16:9\" data-autoinsert=\"true\" data-disable-jsonld=\"true\"><\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <a class=\"video-block__credit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/c\/saltinourhair?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"YouTube Salt in our Hair\">\n                    <div class=\"socials__item\">\n                        <span class=\"socials__link\">\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-youtube\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-youtube\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <span>Subscribe to our <b>YouTube channel<\/b> and never miss a video!<\/span>\n                <\/a>\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__bg\">\n                    <img class=\"video-block__bg-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133228\/Thumb-peru-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Peru\" height=\"450\" width=\"800\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Day 13: Sacred Valley<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After acclimatizing in <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Cusco (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/cusco\/\" target=\"_blank\">Cusco<\/a>, go into incredible Sacred Valley. Discover sights like the Moray circular terraces, Pisac, Maras Salt Mines, and Ollantaytambo. Finally, take the train from Ollantaytambo to Aguas Calientes, better known as Machu Picchu town. Spending the night in Aguas Calientes allows you to get up early and see the sunrise on the Machu Picchu mountain.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Save on your budget by <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/exploorperu-sacred-valley\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"booking a multi-day Sacred Valley tour (opens in a new tab)\">booking a multi-day Sacred Valley tour<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130916\/peru-travel-guide-Moray-Terraces-sacred-valley-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"peru travel guide Moray Terraces sacred valley\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" h