-peru\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Jungle tour through the Peruvian Amazon<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"peru travel amazon village\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"peru travel amazon village\" class=\"wp-image-17181 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833\/peru-travel-amazon-village-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130833