he bigger cities although it&#x2019;s good noticing that the busses are really good and you&#x2019;ll meet people easier.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/peru\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a bus company here<\/a><br data-rich-text-line-break=\"true\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/skyscanner\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Find flights here (opens in a new tab)\">Find the best flights here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130811\/peru-guide-transportation.jpg\" alt=\"peru guide transportation\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"peru guide transportation\" class=\"wp-image-17191 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130811\/peru-guide-transportation.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130811\/peru-guide-transportation-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130811\/peru-guide-transportation-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130811\/peru-guide-transportation-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130