ring these months.<br><br>Tourism-wise the peaks are July and August so you might want to avoid these months of the year.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"best season peru\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best season peru\" class=\"wp-image-17193 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130803\/best-season-travel-peru-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c